  "design_notes": "The chart is designed for a casual StepMania player on an Easy difficulty. It features intuitive quarter-note rhythms in the intro and outro, transitioning to comfortable eighth-note streams during the main drops. Crossovers, jacks, and footswitches have been completely omitted to maintain a relaxed physical flow. Sustains are introduced during vocal phrases and strong melody extensions, while jumps are sparsely placed only on major downbeats.",
